<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:15:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中俄在南海举行海军实弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-kick-off-live-fire-naval-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-07-17/</link><description>据官方媒体《环球时报》报道，中国和俄罗斯已开始在南海进行实弹海军演习，在美国对两国实施制裁后，两国近年来加强了军事和贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-russia-kick-off-live-fire-naval-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>降息呼声金价创历史新高，特朗普言论冲击台湾股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-17/</link><description>周三，随着市场为全球利率下跌做好准备，金价创下历史新高，债券上涨，而在美国总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普对台湾防御的承诺表现冷淡后，台湾股市下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国努力吸引外国游客，但对一些人来说却很难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-strives-lure-foreign-tourists-its-hard-sell-some-2024-07-17/</link><description>吉列尔梅·卡瓦略本月首次访华，意大利人表示，此行的主要因素之一是疫情后取消部分游客入境许可的政策。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-strives-lure-foreign-tourists-its-hard-sell-some-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称台湾应支付国防费导致台积电股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-shares-fall-more-than-2-after-trump-says-taiwan-should-pay-defence-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，台湾应该向美国支付国防费用，因为它没有给美国带来任何东西，这导致台湾芯​​片制造商台积电的股价周三下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-shares-fall-more-than-2-after-trump-says-taiwan-should-pay-defence-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美元因美联储降息而波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-wobbles-with-fed-rate-cuts-back-view-2024-07-17/</link><description>由于美国零售销售数据好于预期，美元周三涨跌互现，交易员关注美联储最早在 9 月份降息的前景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-wobbles-with-fed-rate-cuts-back-view-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国将于八月发布限制中国汽车软件的拟议规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-issue-proposed-rules-limiting-chinese-vehicle-software-august-2024-07-17/</link><description>一位高级官员周二表示，美国商务部计划下个月发布有关联网汽车的拟议规则，并预计对中国和其他被视为对手的国家制造的一些软件施加限制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:08:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-issue-proposed-rules-limiting-chinese-vehicle-software-august-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国潜在禁令的临近，特朗普表示“我支持 TikTok”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-im-tiktok-potential-us-ban-looms-2024-07-16/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，他支持 TikTok，尽管如果中国母公司字节跳动未能剥离这款短视频应用的美国资产，可能会面临禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 23:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-im-tiktok-potential-us-ban-looms-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>分析人士称，特朗普的副总统人选万斯指出了强硬的对华政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-vp-pick-vance-points-tough-china-policy-analysts-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>分析人士表示，唐纳德·特朗普选择民粹主义俄亥俄州参议员万斯作为他的副总统竞选伙伴，进一步证明了美国在特朗普第二届政府中对中国将采取强硬立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-vp-pick-vance-points-tough-china-policy-analysts-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人郭在美国欺诈审判中被判有罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/jury-reaches-verdict-exiled-chinese-businessman-guos-us-fraud-trial-2024-07-16/</link><description>郭文贵是一位流亡的中国商人，也是北京共产党政府的直言不讳的反对者，周二在美国的审判中被判有罪，罪名是从网上追随者那里窃取数亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/jury-reaches-verdict-exiled-chinese-businessman-guos-us-fraud-trial-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国支出减少拖累欧洲奢侈品股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-reduced-spending-saps-european-luxury-stocks-2024-07-16/</link><description>Hugo Boss 的盈利预警和历峰集团 (Richemont) 在中国的疲软销售进一步证明中国人对奢侈品的需求可能已经达到顶峰，从而打压了周二的股价，而保时捷在全球第二大经济体中的投资也令投资者感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:36:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-reduced-spending-saps-european-luxury-stocks-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟国家在投票中对中国电动汽车关税存在分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-members-give-mixed-view-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>了解投票情况的消息人士周二表示，欧盟各国政府在一次不具约束力但仍有影响力的投票中，就欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进口关税的优点提出了分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-members-give-mixed-view-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟可能降低大众和宝马的中国电动汽车进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>两位知情人士称，欧盟委员会已向大众汽车和宝马发出信号，可能会考虑降低这两家汽车制造商进口中国制造的电动汽车的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国紫金矿业拟收购加拿大澜起黄金9.9%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zijin-mining-take-99-stake-canadas-montage-gold-2024-07-16/</link><description>加拿大矿业公司蒙太奇黄金公司周二表示，中国矿业公司紫金矿业集团将通过私募方式获得该公司 9.9% 的战略股权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zijin-mining-take-99-stake-canadas-montage-gold-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，普华永道考虑将中国金融服务审计人员减半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</link><description>两名知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 正在考虑将其在中国的金融服务审计人员裁减至多一半，原因是监管调查和客户流失使业务前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国国有券商将扩大在东南亚的投资银行业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</link><description>国有券商中国银河证券 (CGS) 的一名高级管理人员表示，计划明年将其在东南亚的投资银行团队从目前的 30 人扩大到 50 人，并押注在市场低迷的情况下该地区的交易量会增加在家里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>